==English==

===Etymology===
First attested [[w:1875|1875]], from neuter of {{LL.}} [[moratorius]] "delaying", from {{L.}} [[morari ]] "to delay," from [[mora]] "delay." The word had been written in italics up until [[w:1914|1914]]. See also [[moratory]].

===Noun===
